---
title: Transactional Outbox Pattern
id: 3a5c534a-9f46-4c4b-8fdc-6e12010e1d8b
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant CallbackAPI as Callback API
    participant MetadataService as Metadata Service
    participant MongoSession as MongoDB Session
    participant StatusCol as status collection
    participant MetadataCol as uploadMetadata collection
    participant OutboxCol as outbox collection
    participant OutboxProcessor as Outbox Processor
    participant SNS as AWS SNS

    Note over CallbackAPI,MetadataService: Phase 1 — Atomic Write (single transaction)

    CallbackAPI->>MetadataService: persistMetadataWithOutbox(payload)
    MetadataService->>MongoSession: startSession()
    MetadataService->>MongoSession: withTransaction()

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over MongoSession,OutboxCol: All-or-nothing: commit together or rollback together

        MongoSession->>MetadataService: transaction started
        MetadataService->>MetadataService: formatInboundMetadata(payload)
        MetadataService->>MetadataService: buildValidatedStatusDocuments()

        MetadataService->>StatusCol: insertStatus(statusDocs, session)
        StatusCol-->>MetadataService: acknowledged ✓

        MetadataService->>MetadataCol: insertMany(documents, session)
        MetadataCol-->>MetadataService: insertedIds ✓

        MetadataService->>OutboxCol: createOutboxEntries(insertedIds, docs, session)
        Note right of OutboxCol: status: PENDING<br/>attempts: 0
        OutboxCol-->>MetadataService: acknowledged ✓

        MongoSession->>MongoSession: COMMIT
    end

    MetadataService->>MongoSession: endSession()
    MetadataService-->>CallbackAPI: insertedCount + insertedIds

    Note over OutboxProcessor,SNS: Phase 2 — Background delivery (polling loop)

    loop Every outboxIntervalMs
        OutboxProcessor->>OutboxCol: getProcessableOutboxEntries()
        Note right of OutboxCol: WHERE status = PENDING<br/>OR (status = FAILED AND<br/>attempts < maxAttempts)
        OutboxCol-->>OutboxProcessor: pending batch

        alt No pending entries
            OutboxProcessor->>OutboxProcessor: skip (wait for next poll)
        else Entries found
            loop Batches of 10
                OutboxProcessor->>OutboxProcessor: buildDocumentUploadMessageBatch()<br/>(CloudEvents v1.0 format)
                OutboxProcessor->>SNS: publishBatch(messages)
                SNS-->>OutboxProcessor: Successful[] + Failed[]

                rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
                    Note over OutboxProcessor,OutboxCol: Update transaction
                    OutboxProcessor->>OutboxCol: SENT entries → status: SENT
                    OutboxProcessor->>MetadataCol: set publishedAt timestamp
                    OutboxProcessor->>OutboxCol: FAILED entries → status: FAILED<br/>(error message, increment attempts)
                end
            end
        end
    end
